        <div class="item-page"> 
         <h2> Welcome to the Office of the Treasurer </h2> 
         <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #ff0000;"></span>&nbsp;</p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-family: georgia,palatino;">************************************************ </span></p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;"><span style="color: #3366ff; background-color: #ffffff;">The Office of the Treasurer is located on the first floor of </span></span></span></p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;"><span style="color: #3366ff; background-color: #ffffff;">Bond Hall in Room 112.</span></span></span></p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;"><span style="color: #3366ff; background-color: #ffffff;">Office Hours</span></span></span></p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;"><span style="color: #3366ff; background-color: #ffffff;">Monday - Friday 9:00am til 5:00pm</span></span></span></p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;"><span style="color: #3366ff; background-color: #ffffff;"></span></span>&nbsp;</span></p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino;">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 18pt;"><span style="color: #3366ff;">Please contact us with any questions or concerns</span></span></span></p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;"><span style="color: #3366ff;">you have about your student account.</span></span></span></p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino;"><span style="color: #3366ff; font-size: 18pt;"><span style="background-color: #ffffff;"></span><span style="background-color: #ffffff;">Phone 843-953-5254 / Fax 843-953-6992</span></span></span></p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino;"><strong><span style="color: #3366ff; font-size: 18pt;"><span style="background-color: #ffffff;"></span></span></strong>&nbsp;</span></p> 
         <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: georgia,palatino;"><strong><span style="color: #3366ff; font-size: 18pt;"><span style="background-color: #ffffff;"></span></span></strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;"> <script type="text/javascript">
 <!--
